#' \item{count_decisions}{\\code\{numeric\}. The number of decisions issued by
#' the Commission in the case. Based on the corrected data.}
#' \item{count_lfn_258}{\\code\{numeric\}. The number of letters of formal
#' notice sent by the Commission under Article 258 of the Treaty on the
